<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
  <h1 class="font-bold text-4xl text-center mb-8">About Multipost</h1>

  <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
      At Multipost, we're on a mission to simplify social media management for creators, businesses, and marketers.
      We believe that creating and sharing content should be efficient, allowing you to focus on what matters most -
      engaging with your audience and growing your online presence.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">What We Offer</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
      <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded p-4">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl mb-2">Multi-Platform Publishing</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Create content once and publish it across all your social networks with customization for each platform.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded p-4">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl mb-2">Content Calendar</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Plan and schedule your posts with our intuitive drag-and-drop calendar interface.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded p-4">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl mb-2">Analytics Dashboard</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Track performance across platforms with unified analytics and custom reporting.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded p-4">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl mb-2">Team Collaboration</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Work together with role-based permissions, approval workflows, and shared assets.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Our Story</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
      Multipost was founded in 2023 by a team of social media professionals who were frustrated with
      the complexity and time-consuming nature of managing multiple social accounts. We built the tool
      we wished existed - one that combines power with simplicity.
    </p>
    <p class="text-gray-700">
      Today, we're proud to help thousands of users save time and improve their social media presence
      through our constantly evolving platform.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="text-center">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">Ready to streamline your social media workflow?</h2>

    <% if user_signed_in? %>
    <p class="mb-4">You're already part of the Multipost family. Thank you for your trust!</p>
    <a href="#" class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-lg inline-block transition-colors">Go to Dashboard</a>
    <% else %>
    <div class="flex justify-center space-x-4">
      <%= link_to "Get Started", new_user_registration_path, class: "bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-lg transition-colors" %>
      <%= link_to "Contact Us", pages_contact_path, class: "bg-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-300 px-6 py-2 rounded-lg transition-colors" %>
    </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
